Package model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DatabaseReader
    Interface for any database reader.
    IModel
    Interface to implement to the GUI Model.
    InvestmentStrategy
    Interface to implement the Investment strategy of a portfolio.
    Portfolio
    Interface for portfolio which mentions the important methods suppoerted by different types of portfolio.
    StockAPI
    Interface class which should be implemented by all the classes that make API calls to get stock details.
    StockInterface
    Interface for the Stocks.
    StockMarketModelInterface
    Interface that contains all the functions a stock market should implement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlphaVantageAPI
    Class that implements stockAPI using AlphaVantage.
    DollarCost
    Class that determines Dollar cost of a portfolio.
    FlexiblePortfolio
    Class that describes a portfolio object and its related functions.
    getEvaluation
    Class to get the Evaluation of a portfolio.
    InflexiblePortfolio
    Class that describes a portfolio object and its related functions.
    Investor
    Class that represents an investor, it stores the investor name and the portfolio he has.
    JsonReader
    Class that is has functionalities to read a json file.
    Model
    Class to implement model of the GUI.
    PortfolioPerformance
    Class to calculate portfolio performance.
    Stock
    Class that represents a stock.
    StockMarketModel
    Class for having stockMarket related functions, responsible to fetch data from database, and update userdata.
    StrategyPortfolio
    Class to implement Strategic Investment of Portfolio.
    WeightedStock
    Class to implement Weighted Stocks.
    YahooAPI
    Class that uses yahoo finance API to get details about the stocks.
